/**
The Novice Programmer ~ EP01 Bubble Sort 
**/

YouTube: http://youtu.be/GZpTgRFdPQs

In the first episode, we take a look at implementing a simple bubble sort algorithm. We iterate through the design of the application we write the code, and discuss the advantages and disadvantages of the design decisions made.

Language used for the project: Java
About the algorithm: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bubble_sort
Link to the Reddit discussion thread: http://www.reddit.com/r/learnprogramming/comments/1vmra3/the_novice_programmer_ep01_bubble_sort/